                    "value": "Scope and Contents"
                },
                "p": [
                    {
                        "value": "This small collection contains flyers and correspondence concerning organizations Marc Edelman was involved in, particularly the New York Civil Liberties Union and Reelpolitik (a Columbia University film collective). Also included is one file containing correspondence regarding a student riot at the High School of Music and Art and an issue of the \u003cspan class=\"ead-emph ead-emph-italic\"\u003eWashington Free Press\u003c/span\u003e dealing with Students for a Democratic Society (SDS) action against the Pentagon."
                    }
                ]
            }
